node.text: Grace wanted rotisserie chicken, mashed potatoes and macaroni & cheese. I made everything in my Anyday containers except the chicken which I bought. Never throw away your rotisserie chicken scraps! Made a quick tasty gravy with a roux, @momolongplay savory salt, a little sprig of frozen thyme, and button mushroom that needed to get used or thrown away. Gravy used to smother the chicken. I will try and do a video or something with recipes for everything (but maybe this will also never happen because I’m lazy).

node.title: Did you know you can make a gravy in the microwave + @cookanyday?
